Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This court finds the defendant,{\i}\N{\i1}Jolyne Cujoh…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So what did you do?\NWhy did you get thrown in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:22.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,…shall be confined to\NGreen Dolphin Street State Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.78,Main,,0,0,0,,for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out you have an ability.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Stone Free."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll break free{\i}\N{\i1}from this sea of stone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 3: THE VISITOR (1)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Stone Free.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}When unraveled, this thread can reach far.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}However, it becomes less powerful{\i}\N{\i1}and inflicts less damage.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it bundles, it hardens.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its reach is reduced to about two meters.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I break through the bars{\i}\N{\i1}with Stone Free?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it lacked the strength to do so.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most it could do was this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mental energy is harnessed{\i}\N{\i1}using the stone inside the charm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like to get out of here{\i}\N{\i1}using this power,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now's not the time yet.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, I need to learn{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all I can about this place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you lend me some change?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got some in my room,\Nbut the call is about to disconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:12.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I can pay you back as soon as I'm done.\NA dollar is all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't spoken to my family in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks! You saved my skin!\NI'll pay you back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Move, bitch! Don't try to cut in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:34.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for her\Nto finish for 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you waiting in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Dumbass, you must be new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got to reserve\Nthese phones in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,No one told me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, now you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, the reservations\Nare made a month in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.22,Main,,0,0,0,,A month?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Why should I wait a whole month\Nfor a few minutes of phone time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what's strange\Nabout prison, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll buy that spot\Non the phone from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,And this is the cause of the phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to call her.{\i}\N{\i1}I need to hear her voice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The voice of my mom…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut your trap! Keep away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I already told you I'm through with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't push me away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You messed up big time just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You just lent a dollar\Nto that blondie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get her to pay you back right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, your life here will be over\Nif you don't get it back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NOf course, she'll pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It was just a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you said "just a dollar"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You're digging your own grave\Nwith that mentality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,At the Aquarium,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.17,Main,,0,0,0,,lending or borrowing money between inmates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,is one thing\Nyou should avoid at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's say that you fail\Nto get the dollar back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll become a bottom feeder like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Jolyne the newbie\Ncouldn't even extort back her dollar."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The rumor will spread like wildfire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,and you'll be the target in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,One after another, every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Once you're out of money, you'll be forced\Nto give your body and even your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:37.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what hell on earth is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I, now? It was\N"just a dollar" for her at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,See that blonde from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She went to her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,but she's not planning on\Ncoming down for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this one's a classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to pay me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A dollar, right? I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all in my head, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you have the money in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You went back, right?\NDo you have it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I said I'll give it back later.\NI don't have it now, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You a tightwad or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, can you lend me ten more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I can call up friends on the outside\Nand ask for more money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Please? You've got to have some on you.\NCome on, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you hurry it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the dollar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,-Please!\N-You'll pay me later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll buy the time from you!\NI'll pay five… No, ten dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That'll be ten dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Go use the bathroom next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone else will have\Nthe urge to use it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's up to you whether you can get\Nyour money back, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What the… What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, I'll be leaving soon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow, I'll get out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Inmate number FE40536.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm returning to my cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Please unlock this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,you will have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But you must not meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You must not go to the visitation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.30,Main,,0,0,0,,you and others will be in grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A fate more terrible than death\Nwill happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who was that just now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did a child sneak in here?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear my order to standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not touch the bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I said do not grab the bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,A visitor is coming tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to see you, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.10,Main,,0,0,0,,but someone in the next building,\Nyou know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,you got it on backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Your pants, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about yesterday, FE40536.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's your fault\Nfor grabbing onto the bars like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I had already let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But you still hit me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Did you mutter something?\NCouldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind. How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand up. I'll handcuff you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,A visitor? Who is it, my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,How the hell should I know?\NGive me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand on the mark right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You have 30 minutes.\NYou are allowed to hold hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.22,Main,,0,0,0,,but kissing or undressing are not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You will receive anything\Nthey bring after the visitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Foreign languages are forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Depending on the visit,\Nthe guard may choose to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait there until you're authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Turn around. Go back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,How did a child like you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand either,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.68,Main,,0,0,0,,but there are some things\Nmore fearsome than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's happening at this very prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,So please turn back. Go back to your cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No. My mom must be here to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,She must be missing me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to let her know\Nthat I'm doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Then take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It should protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,FE40536, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These are bones!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop dawdling. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:54.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, did you receive the charm\NI asked your mom to give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STAND NAME: STAR PLATINUM\NSTAND MASTER: JOTARO KUJO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Car and wallet theft. Assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,This must be some mistake!\NMy Jolyne would never…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Since she's only 14,\Nshe won't be charged this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You're headed to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This is your daughter we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Why not go tomorrow instead?\NAnd you call yourself her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's the pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd rather receive disciplinary action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Had I known it was you,\NI wouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Shit, I hit him too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It was not your boyfriend Romeo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,who conspired to frame you for murder\Nand had you sent to this prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,This man is incarcerated\Nin the men's prison here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,He's ex-military.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A veteran sniper who could hit his mark\Nunder any difficult circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,According to the report,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.67,Main,,0,0,0,,his vision has deteriorated\Ndue to cataracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,This man was behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Even that manslaughter accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A henchman of Johngalli A.{\i}\N{\i1}kidnapped an innocent hitchhiker{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and threw him in front of the car.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He also hired a greedy lawyer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to set up the trust-fund baby.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johngalli A. was pulling the strings{\i}\N{\i1}from this prison.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me, Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a "plea deal" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,This court finds the defendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.04,Main,,0,0,0,,-Jolyne Cujoh…\N-{\i1}Fifteen years…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You hit me twice yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would he plot my imprisonment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,-Sit.\N-Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I said sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen. Johngalli A.'s target\Nwas you all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so that he can eliminate you\Nany time he wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,within these prison walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is he after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Because you are my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You are of the Joestar bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Joestar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The Joestar bloodline\Ncan be traced back hundreds of decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And Johngalli A. plots to\Ntake revenge on our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We are endowed with\Nthe wonderful gift to move others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But at times,\Npowerful emotions leave dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dregs called grudges, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:16:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,In the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I defeated a mortal enemy{\i}\N{\i1}of the Joestar clan.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. is a pawn of this enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We've never met,\Nbut I have no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Though it's been over 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Johngalli A. uses his fanaticism\Nfor this man to exact his revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. I thought\Nyou were just a marine biologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about enemies and grudges?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Just know that you are being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We will bypass the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you acquired your Stand yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Stand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.51,Main,,0,0,0,,As my daughter, you are predisposed\Nto the ability to use this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you see any changes\Nfrom the pendant I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It seems you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the Stand ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand… Then you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Use your power to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit your yapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't try to act like a father now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're finally here to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What, because you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I've already forgotten about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll keep that shocking story\Nand the Stand ability in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't ever visit me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My handcuffs!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I get out of them?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The brand is different.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The guard didn't even approach the table.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, get away from that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Star Platinum: The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Time, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What the fuck? did I just get shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay still! The fight has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the layout to the right?\NAny windows in that direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Two or three. But they're all barred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a real bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This bullet, called a Sniper Premium,\Nis specific to rifles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The shot was undoubtedly\Ntaken by Johngalli A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I thought he was an inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Inmates are prohibited\Nfrom even having pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\NBut guns can be disassembled, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Precise parts may be snuck in{\i}\N{\i1}through various objects.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guards can be bribed by his henchmen{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the objects won't get searched.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Little by little, slowly but surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,But we're in the women's prison!\NHe can't possibly shoot me from the men's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We're inside a building.\NThere are obstructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,A rifle and an ability make that possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.20,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, Johngalli A. is,\Nwithout a doubt, a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Certainly, that's not just some rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems really light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just floating in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't engage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,First, we must know what it can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I said don't engage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Can it see my thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It's reacting to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.58,Main,,0,0,0,,However, not to the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Its movement seems unrelated\Nto the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, could it be reacting to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What was it called?\NThe change in the air from the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, the movement of the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Aerodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It detected our positions\Nusing aerodynamics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, so he knows our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,But how can he shoot us\Nfrom the men's dormitory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, you were saved\Nby a fortuitous accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not make a move\Nuntil we understand the contraption.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,-I know that!\N-You… FE40536!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're done for, I'll have you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it? Jolyne Cujoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.54,Main,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-It's headed towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:42.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you get disciplined!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,After I beat you to death, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, don't leave the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! And don't order me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's knock him out\Nbefore we get into more trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn you, who do you think\Nyou're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:46.38,Main,,0,0,0,,
